# MIG Master

> MIG Flash backup tools and compatible Nintendo Switch accessories

MIG Master offers MIG Flash V2, MIG Flash Dumper, and compatible Nintendo Switch accessories. The store focuses on clear compatibility information, practical setup guidance, and reliable support for customers managing personal backups of games they legally own.

## Collections

- [Featured products](https://migmaster.shop/a/shop/collections/frontpage): Best-selling MIG Master products and compatible Nintendo Switch accessories.

## Products

- [Mig Flash Dumper — USB-C Switch Game Cartridge Reader](https://migmaster.shop/a/shop/products/mig-flash-dumper): Mig Flash Dumper — USB-C Switch Game Cartridge Reader is a USB-C game-cartridge reader created for owners who want a practical way to make personal backups of compatible Nintendo Switch cartridges they legally own. It works as the preparation companion to Mig Flash V2, reading cartridge data for backup on a computer before the files are organized on a microSD card. The Dumper is a separate accessory and is not required for every Mig Flash V2 workflow, but it offers a more direct and repeatable cartridge reading process.
- [Mig Flash V2 — Switch Game Backup Cartridge with Toggle Button](https://migmaster.shop/a/shop/products/mig-flash-v2): The Mig Flash V2 is a Switch game backup cartridge with a toggle button on the top for switching between games. It works the same as the original Mig Flash but includes a quality-of-life update: a quick press switches to the next game, a long press to the previous one.
- [Portable Charger Case for Switch 2 — 10000mAh Battery Pack with Stand](https://migmaster.shop/a/shop/products/portable-charger-case-for-nintendo-switch-2-10000mah-external-rechargeable-battery-pack-with-foldable-stand-and-2-game-card-storage): The Portable Charger Case for Switch 2 — 10000mAh Battery Pack with Stand is an all-in-one power bank and ergonomic grip for Nintendo Switch 2, featuring a 10,000mAh capacity (dual 5,000mAh cells) providing approximately 1.4x extra charges and up to double the original play time, plus a built-in foldable stand and 2 game card storage slots.
- [AOLION K20 Hall Effect Gaming Controller — Zero Drift, Mechanical Buttons, Custom Macros](https://migmaster.shop/a/shop/products/game-controller): AOLION K20 Hall Effect Gaming Controller — Zero Drift, Mechanical Buttons, Custom Macros — AOLION K20 Hall Effect Gaming Controller — Zero Drift, Mechanical Buttons, Custom Macros
